netimage_ecos.c implements the receiving part of the netimage tools
for the eCos operating system. It requires an ecos configuration with
tcp/ip networking and a vga output device.

Installation:

1. Point the HW_DESIGN environment variable to your EDK design.

2. Run 'make setup' to build the eCos library.

3. Run 'make' to build the ELF executable

4. Download the executable to the target.

